    <item>
      <title>马杜罗加大委内瑞拉镇压力度，引起邻国愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/maduro-ratchets-up-repression-ahead-of-inauguration-in-venezuela</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉政府加大了镇压力度，引发了其最亲密盟友之一的抗议，反对派计划本周在全国范围内举行示威活动，反对尼古拉斯·马杜罗就任总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/maduro-ratchets-up-repression-ahead-of-inauguration-in-venezuela</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 13:28:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国无法投保的房屋正在酝酿一场新的金融危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/features/2024-home-insurance-real-estate-crisis/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着私人保险公司退出加利福尼亚州至佛罗里达州等最容易受到气候灾害影响的美国市场，“最后手段”州房屋保险计划正承担着数万亿美元的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/features/2024-home-insurance-real-estate-crisis/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 00:00:04 GMT</pubDate>
